nt extend BaseIdentifiableObject but neither\ntable has a `name` column, and the hbm mappings don't expose one. Dormant\ntoday because no CRUD controller lists these entities, but any query that\nsorts by displayName/name would crash after PR #22395 moved ordering into\nJPA criteria.\n\n- Add `name` column to oauth2_authorization + oauth2_authorization_consent\n  (varchar(230), NOT NULL, backfilled from principal_name).\n- Map `name` in both hbm files.\n- Derive entity.name from principalName in both service toEntity methods\n  via StringUtils.left(..., 230), since Spring's OAuth2Authorization and\n  OAuth2AuthorizationConsent have no name field.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"2f514ce73bd3d20204b69a841c6b906f5e30669b","tree_id":"f907c3065930e38b43472e2d622045f693672f52","timestamp":"2026-04-21T06:14:15Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https